{"tid":1182921,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼妹終於跳BP啲歌上節目,真係睇到香港反韓人士反晒白眼!","createTime":"2019-06-02T13:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T16:57:18.000Z","uid":56701,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77f7fb3aa626f086a34f5b6005db9bd88fbec296","tid":1182921,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a8at8zm68kM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da8at8zm68kM&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=779a417a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a8at8zm68kM</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地反韓人士一致認為佢地係整左容假扮既外國人嚟...</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Emvjbd3BCs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEmvjbd3BCs8&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=a52aba0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Emvjbd3BCs8</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">仲唔俾我捉到你啲泡菜揾假鬼扮到KPOP好流行!啲黑鬼求其揾個人搽黑佢咪得囉!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KXXB50dWDwI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKXXB50dWDwI&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=d49ae677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KXXB50dWDwI</a><br />\n片尾隻黑鬼仲做戲喊苦喊忽好感動咁...特約演員都係演員嚟,俾啲認真好唔好,見到偶像就喊!我地香港人(反韓)肯定唔接受呢啲婆媽嘢!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_m1rHGnNvfM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_m1rHGnNvfM&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=db34783b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_m1rHGnNvfM</a><br />\n跳埋隻歌係歐美紅少少就揾黑白奶一齊跳...你睇個泰妹O晒咀咁幾假!啲奶假咖!<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地香港反韓人士肯肯定定啲韓流係做假既....佢地全部係特約演員嚟!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地睇返<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港流行經典50 年</span>好過啦...果啲先叫真音樂!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>以上百份百係反韓人士心聲!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed9497cee08a69c0a9ee9767e5078381a01ee19","tid":1182921,"uid":56701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人就係反韓!<br />\n香港人就係反韓!<br />\n香港人就係反韓!<br />\n好重要所以要講三次!</strong></span>"},{"pid":"59fa78e30aed0e05fed619279bd199cca996b60d","tid":1182921,"uid":61498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"有band一路跳bp一路玩metal未？"},{"pid":"62c98f6e86c1bcb61c4fd2aacdcfacf6727a06e6","tid":1182921,"uid":29702,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf0368aef5a156c060c593ffc8437b06044b0110","tid":1182921,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59fa78e30aed0e05fed619279bd199cca996b60d","tid":1182921,"uid":61498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"有band一路跳bp一路玩metal未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..就算有都係無乜欣賞價值...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地香港人最叻係坐响張按摩椅開著個土炮HI-FI聲嘢焚機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69129a90856e6a12fae1b662c8379298ceeb4ef","tid":1182921,"uid":61498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf0368aef5a156c060c593ffc8437b06044b0110","tid":1182921,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59fa78e30aed0e05fed619279bd199cca996b60d","tid":1182921,"uid":61498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"有band一路跳bp一路玩metal未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..就算有都係無乜欣賞價值...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地香港人最叻係坐响張按摩椅開著個土炮HI-FI聲嘢焚機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"冇片好難講有冇欣賞價值"},{"pid":"1836a63bac1c73a8496ef6f3bb10b62f5bcafb0b","tid":1182921,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">突發! 千祈咪睇日本妹跳果段...後果自負...</span></span></strong><br />\n我而家要入急症室洗眼先!"},{"pid":"08cc3ae57fd5594d0bc9fc239c5346fa2f33df9c","tid":1182921,"uid":56701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AVqcb9xMG2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAVqcb9xMG2w&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=e23d051c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AVqcb9xMG2w</a><br />\n反韓都要講吓佢地竟然造馬俾德國隊贏,擺明同我地香港過唔去啦...德國竟然幫手收埋兩個香港人...證明呢啲爛鬼國家先會鐘意KPOP...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地香港人最醒所以反韓人士比例上係最多...仲有日本人去你度參賽老屈人地輸真係可恥...擺明落我地香港面啦...我地大部份人聽日本歌大咖嘛...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">泡菜真係好過份!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b43045112441a2209d9e5e28c3ba73870d7af4b","tid":1182921,"uid":52264,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62c98f6e86c1bcb